 MBOMBELA – Devland Cash and Carry has added a retail hyper division to its store. The new division is aptly named Devland Hyper. Devland has been in the Lowveld’s fast-moving consumer goods (FMCG) wholesale sector for the past seven years. Hamzah, Isa and Sameeha Naby. ALSO READ: WATCH: The annual Uplands Festival was a feast for the ears

As the Devland Group, it has always been their intention to venture into the retail sector, offering customers only the best brands, at the best prices. This FMCG wholesaler enterprise provides general merchandise and food products to a range of independent traders and commercial users. New Devland Hyper store ready to serve Mbombelans. Devland prides itself on providing cost-effective prices and excellent customer service. It offers various products ranging from beverages, groceries, perishables, fruits and vegetables, to commodities, cosmetics, bath and baby, toiletries, toys and sweets. The retail store is open Monday to Thursday from 08:00 to 17:00, and closed between 13:00 and 14:00. Zodwa Ngoma. ALSO READ: Vuur en vlam in die warm hart van die Laeveld!

On Friday they are open from 08:00 to 17:00 and closed between 12:00 and 14:00. On weekends, Devland Hyper is open from 08:00 to 13:00 on Saturday and on selected Sundays and public holidays. To experience its great service while enjoying amazing specials, visit the store at 6-8 Old Pretoria Road, next to Buco.